371
00:20:04,065 --> 00:20:06,628
Oh, we're just talking here,

372
00:20:07,207 --> 00:20:09,992
but I think 150...

373
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,696
would probably get you a deal.

374
00:20:13,775 --> 00:20:15,042
Maybe even...

375
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:17,076
175.

376
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:31,780
So...

377
00:20:31,781 --> 00:20:34,237
Was I right about Larry?

378
00:20:34,769 --> 00:20:36,255
Yes, Peter.

379
00:20:36,333 --> 00:20:39,758
Mr. Popler's leaking
information to Frobisher's camp.

380
00:20:39,895 --> 00:20:41,303
How do you know?

381
00:20:41,585 --> 00:20:44,433
I gave him 175 as a settlement number.

382
00:20:44,451 --> 00:20:47,155
Ray fiske brought it right back to me.

383
00:20:49,282 --> 00:20:51,269
So what are you going to do?

